{"tid":1894513,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦不時重新開機 好撚麻煩","createTime":"2020-02-24T03:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T12:06:56.000Z","uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c443f23adc10864fb53a83a60b09ddea74566b5a","tid":1894513,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"個問題搞左好耐都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求巴打幫幫手<br />\n3個月前買左2080S Waterforce同埋M.2 SSD, 裝機果陣諗住順便清塵, 連CPU都拆埋落黎順便換散熱膏<br />\n<br />\n頭一兩個星期我無印象有冇事, 但之後我部機每隔一段時間就會斷電式咁熄左所有野黑哂, 然後Display白燈著左, Display風扇全速狂轉唔停(類似開機入BIOS之前POST咁樣)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就會hold住係呢度, 白燈著左風扇狂轉之後乜都無反應, 夾硬按機箱開機掣十幾秒都熄唔到, 要捐枱底去熄火牛/電掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個問題出現頻率都好奇怪 通常過左24小時之後先會出現(部機開24/7), 但都有試過係24小時內出現兩次或以上, 但次數好少<br />\n<br />\n跟住交叉測試過好多件, 換左新火牛850w, 換返舊Display, Ram逐條試, 重新插過M.2, 掹左Reset針位兩條線, 所有測試後問題一樣存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家應該點做先可以無事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇高手係度呀"},{"pid":"5894926e6bc0ba974b0f906451b9a69f66095835","tid":1894513,"uid":236574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會板有問題？"},{"pid":"2966b7b6066aefc868c0bc7f09dcf9316730bee5","tid":1894513,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5894926e6bc0ba974b0f906451b9a69f66095835","tid":1894513,"uid":236574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會板有問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"我成日都係咁, 每次想清潔吓部機底板就會壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fb63fe37676738ae432952f8881e512e0e67d2","tid":1894513,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"古語有云 唔識就咪鬼自己清塵<br />\n你塊底板俾你玩死咗啦"},{"pid":"76e4a1f8aebbbeecb70b69aa52791acdf232384e","tid":1894513,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"Cpu過熱？<br />\n試下再換散熱膏"},{"pid":"5395aa54026b66df49759fab5fa9435cd8cf4870","tid":1894513,"uid":33046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:54:12.000Z","msg":"換野個陣可能整到塊板"},{"pid":"a11198fa9ab49dc6899c22ccd3b109bc1db38829","tid":1894513,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01fb63fe37676738ae432952f8881e512e0e67d2","tid":1894513,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"古語有云 唔識就咪鬼自己清塵<br />\n你塊底板俾你玩死咗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"講漏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我第一時間係去左保養度換左塊新板 都係有問題"},{"pid":"369ff7aeadc05cbb4e5ae2bc9afe7fc961bce1d7","tid":1894513,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76e4a1f8aebbbeecb70b69aa52791acdf232384e","tid":1894513,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"Cpu過熱？<br />\n試下再換散熱膏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:35:00.000Z","msg":"應該就唔會 我長期有afterburner睇住<br />\n同埋有時係待機既時候乜都無開都會發生<br />\n不過都Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91545678ff1f42b94f0ee1c4a073bb074865e5ed","tid":1894513,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5894926e6bc0ba974b0f906451b9a69f66095835","tid":1894513,"uid":236574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會板有問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"講漏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去保養換左塊板一樣都係出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc956655791cbfcce5d3d3915b9ba7f436831beb","tid":1894513,"uid":